      <div id="previewArea" class="preview-panel" aria-live="polite">
        <h2 id="previewTitle">About Acme Solutions</h2>
        <div id="previewBody">
          <p>Generate a premium About Us section using the panel on the left. Choose tone, length and template — then click <strong>Generate</strong>.</p>
