      <div id="guideArea" style="display:none">
        <div class="article">
          <h1>How to use the About Us Generator — Complete SEO-optimized guide</h1>
          <p>This guide walks you step-by-step through creating, optimizing and publishing a high-performing About page. It includes best practices, sample structures, on-page SEO tips, schema, and a short FAQ.</p>

          <h2>Why an optimized About page matters</h2>
          <p>The About page builds trust, improves brand perception, and ranks for branded and informational queries. A well-structured page helps search engines understand your business and increases click-through rates from search results.</p>

          <h2>Suggested structure (SEO-friendly)</h2>
          <ol>
            <li><strong>H1 — Brand-focused title:</strong> e.g. "About Acme Solutions" (include brand name).</li>
            <li><strong>Lead paragraph:</strong> One to two sentences summarizing who you are and what you do. Include your primary keyword.</li>
            <li><strong>Mission / Vision:</strong> Clear one-liner describing your purpose.</li>
            <li><strong>What we do / Products & Services:</strong> Short sections with H2-H3 headings for important offerings.</li>
            <li><strong>Values / Team / Process:</strong> Bullet points or short paragraphs for scannability.</li>
            <li><strong>Social proof / Milestones:</strong> Numbers, logos, awards, client quotes if available.</li>
            <li><strong>Call to action:</strong> Contact, learn more, or sign up.</li>
          </ol>

          <h2>On-page SEO checklist</h2>
          <ul>
            <li>Use a descriptive <code>&lt;title&gt;</code> and meta description that include your brand and primary keyword.</li>
            <li>Include structured headings (H1 → H2 → H3).</li>
            <li>Use natural language for keywords; avoid stuffing. Include 2–3 relevant long-tail phrases.</li>
            <li>Add internal links to key pages (Products, Contact, Case Studies).</li>
            <li>Optimize images with descriptive <code>alt</code> text and small file sizes.</li>
            <li>Add JSON-LD schema for Organization/LocalBusiness if applicable.</li>
            <li>Ensure mobile-friendly layout and fast load times.</li>
          </ul>

          <h2>SEO-ready example (use as-is or adapt)</h2>
          <div class="code">&lt;h1&gt;About Acme Solutions&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Acme Solutions builds reliable software solutions for small and medium businesses. We combine user-centered design with scalable engineering to help teams grow.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;Our mission&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;To simplify complex problems and deliver measurable outcomes for our clients.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;What we do&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Custom software development&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Consulting&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Managed services&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;Get in touch&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="/contact"&gt;Contact us&lt;/a&gt; to discuss your project.&lt;/p&gt;</div>

          <h2>Advanced tips</h2>
          <p>Implement <strong>canonical</strong> tags if you have multiple language versions; use <strong>hreflang</strong> for localization. Monitor performance with Google Search Console and iterate based on queries and CTRs.</p>

          <h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
          <div class="faq">
            <strong>Q: How long should my About page be?</strong>
            <p>A: Aim for 300–900 words depending on your business complexity. Ensure clarity and easily scannable sections.</p>

            <strong>Q: What keywords should I target?</strong>
            <p>A: Start with branded terms (e.g., "Acme Solutions"), then add informational phrases like "about Acme Solutions", "Acme Solutions mission", and 1–2 service-related keywords.</p>

            <strong>Q: Can I use the generator content as final copy?</strong>
            <p>A: Yes — but personalize it with customer specifics, achievements, and real team details for authenticity.</p>
          </div>

          <h2>Next steps: publish & measure</h2>
          <ol>
            <li>Copy the generated content into your CMS as the canonical About page.</li>
            <li>Add meta title and description, upload optimized images, add JSON-LD Organization schema.</li>
            <li>Submit the page to Google Search Console for faster indexing.</li>
            <li>Monitor search queries and refine content quarterly.</li>
          </ol>

          <p class="small">Need help customizing the guide for your industry? Click "Surprise me" for suggested keywords or ask me to generate a fully tailored About page with sample team bios, milestones, and schema markup.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div style="margin-top:12px;display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;gap:12px">
        <div class="small">Preview — edit directly if you like, then copy or download.</div>
        <div style="display:flex;gap:8px">
          <button class="btn btn-ghost" id="editBtn">Edit</button>
          <button class="btn btn-primary" id="finalizeBtn">Finalize</button>
        </div>
      </div>

